import React from 'react';

import { View, Text, Button, Stack, Spacer } from 'core';

import './App.css';

function App() {
  return (
    <Stack divider padding="medium" spacing="medium" className="App" style={{ maxWidth: 800 }}>
      <Stack horizontal divider spacing="medium">
        <Stack>
          <Text fontSize="xlarge">XLarge (32px)</Text>
          <Spacer fillColor="gray-1" size="small" />
          <Text fontSize="large">Large</Text>
          <Spacer fillColor="gray-1" size="small" />
          <Text fontSize="medium">Medium</Text>
          <Spacer fillColor="gray-1" size="small" />
          <Text>Default</Text>
          <Spacer fillColor="gray-1" size="small" />
          <Text fontSize="small">Small</Text>
        </Stack>
        <Stack>
          <Button title="Hello World" />
        </Stack>
      </Stack>
      <Text>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et
        dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut
        aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum
        dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.
      </Text>
      <Stack horizontal spacing="medium">
        <Text fontSize="large">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur…
        </Text>
        <Text fontSize="medium">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur…
        </Text>
        <Text>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur…
        </Text>
      </Stack>
    </Stack>
  );
}

export default App;
